data.name: grdPaStatus.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.BUNHO , A.PAT_STATUS , B.PAT_STATUS_NAME , A.PAT_STATUS_CODE , C.PAT_STATUS_CODE_NAME , A.MENT , E.SEQ , E.INDISPENSABLE_YN , LTRIM(TO_CHAR(NVL(E.SEQ, 99), '00000'))||A.PAT_STATUS CONT_KEY FROM OCS0802 F, OCS0804 E, OCS0103 D, OCS0802 C, OCS0801 B, OCS1801 A WHERE A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND D.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.PAT_STATUS = A.PAT_STATUS AND C.PAT_STATUS (+) = A.PAT_STATUS AND C.PAT_STATUS_CODE(+) = A.PAT_STATUS_CODE AND D.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND E.PAT_STATUS_GR = D.PAT_STATUS_GR AND E.PAT_STATUS = A.PAT_STATUS AND F.PAT_STATUS (+) = B.PAT_STATUS AND F.PAT_STATUS_CODE(+) = B.DEFAULT_PAT_STATUS_CODE UNION ALL SELECT :f_bunho BUNHO , B.PAT_STATUS , C.PAT_STATUS_NAME , DECODE(B.PAT_STATUS,'02',DECODE(E.SEX,'M','01',NULL) ,'40',DECODE(E.SEX,'M','01',NULL),NULL) PAT_STATUS_CODE , NULL PAT_STATUS_CODE_NAME, B.MENT , B.SEQ , B.INDISPENSABLE_YN , LTRIM(TO_CHAR(NVL(B.SEQ, 99), '00000'))||B.PAT_STATUS CONT_KEY FROM OUT0101 E, OCS0802 D, OCS0801 C, OCS0804 B, OCS0103 A WHERE A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.PAT_STATUS_GR = A.PAT_STATUS_GR AND C.PAT_STATUS = B.PAT_STATUS AND D.PAT_STATUS (+) = C.PAT_STATUS AND D.PAT_STATUS_CODE(+) = C.DEFAULT_PAT_STATUS_CODE AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT 'X' FROM OCS1801 D WHERE D.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND D.PAT_STATUS = B.PAT_STATUS ) AND E.BUNHO = :f_bunho ORDER BY 9

data.name: grdPurpose.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT 'N' , A.CODE_NAME FROM PFE0102 A WHERE A.CODE_TYPE = 'ENDO_PURPOSE' AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code ORDER BY DECODE(FN_CPL_NUM_CHK(A.CODE_NAME_RE), 0, TO_NUMBER(A.CODE_NAME_RE), 999)

data.name: grdComment3.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.COMMENTS , '1' , A.SER FROM OUT0106 A , OCS1003 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.CMMT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.JUNDAL_TABLE = 'PFE' AND A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.FKOCS = B.PKOCS1003 AND B.ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date UNION SELECT A.COMMENTS , '2' , A.SER FROM OUT0106 A , OCS2003 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.CMMT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.JUNDAL_TABLE = 'PFE' AND A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'I' AND A.FKOCS = B.PKOCS2003 AND B.ORDER_DATE = :f_order_date ORDER BY 2, 3

data.name: xLabel3.Text
data.value: 検査の目的 [注意] 500文字未満で入力して下さい。

data.name: dsvDw.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.PKPFE1000 , A.C3 , A.FKOCS , A.BUNHO , A.HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME , A.RESIDENT_YN FROM OCS0103 B, PFE1000 A WHERE A.FKOCS = :f_fkocs AND A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HANGMOG_CODE(+) = A.HANGMOG_CODE

data.name: dsvLDOCS0801.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.PAT_STATUS , A.PAT_STATUS_NAME , B.PAT_STATUS_CODE , B.PAT_STATUS_CODE_NAME , C.INDISPENSABLE_YN FROM OCS0103 D, OCS0804 C, OCS0802 B, OCS0801 A WHERE D.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND C.PAT_STATUS_GR = D.PAT_STATUS_GR AND B.PAT_STATUS = C.PAT_STATUS AND A.PAT_STATUS = B.PAT_STATUS AND D.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code

data.name: layOrderDate.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT B.ORDER_DATE FROM OUT0106 A , OCS1003 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.CMMT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.JUNDAL_TABLE = 'PFE' AND A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.FKOCS = B.PKOCS1003 UNION SELECT B.ORDER_DATE FROM OUT0106 A , OCS2003 B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND A.BUNHO = :f_bunho AND A.CMMT_GUBUN = 'O' AND A.JUNDAL_TABLE = 'PFE' AND A.IN_OUT_GUBUN = 'I' AND A.FKOCS = B.PKOCS2003 ORDER BY 1
